items.title: Learn Yoga Fly like a Butterfly
items.headline: A lighter Approach to Yoga
objectives_summary: Learn Yoga Fly like a butterfly is intended to bring in the lighter side of Yoga for beginners. The common approach to Yoga . Yoga is for all age groups and all fitness groups. It is with an intention to bring Yoga into lives of millions of people in the world, I have created the First ever Lighter Course in Yoga, fly like a butterfly, The course has some unique offerings like the Butterfly song and warm up's, they are intended to bring the non- judgemental child in us, The Course creatively presents the Palm tree posture as the Moods of Palm tree to be wanting to reach the sky, touch the sky and climb the sky, the warrior posture is emanated as Courage posture to give a feeling of the psychological state of an warrior, Each Asana has been worked with numerous students who had no idea of Yoga and today have accepted yoga as an integral part of life. The course includes very basic Postures like, Palmtree posture, The warrior posture, Half moon posture, Air release posture standing and Triangle posture sides. This course is to encourage individuals to come into the space of Yoga without any previous experience and create the ripple of butterfly in your heart to observe the beauty of Nature and learning to lead life with same lightness of a butterfly and I am sure, the course will create a positive impact in your life. Thanking you for connecting to me in this journey. I am here for your sughestions, your wellbeing and most importantly to see the miracle called" us" fly like a Butterfly. So, hop on and we are onto a funfilled and exciting journey together. Please take time to review the course and encourage me to create more exciting courses for all.
